column1: #Text=Morgan Hill is a city in Santa Clara County , California , at the southern tip of Silicon Valley , in the San Francisco Bay Area .
#Text=Morgan Hill is primarily an affluent residential community for Silicon Valley , as well as the seat for several high-tech companies .
#Text=Morgan Hill sits astride US 101 , a major north-south highway that spans the Pacific coast from San Diego to Seattle .
#Text=Commercial air service is via Mineta San Jose International Airport , approximately 20 miles to the north .
#Text=Morgan Hill also is connected to San Jose and San Francisco by Caltrain service , but only during peak commute hours .
#Text=Is the largest state park in northern California .
#Text=It is open year-round for hikers , mountain bikers , backpackers , equestrians , car campers , picnickers , and photographers .
#Text=It is great for hiking , running , biking , and skating on paved trails .
#Text=The lake is open for boating and fishing .

#Text=Used to be a hot spot in the 50s as a restaurant , place to dance , and a bar .
#Text=The Capri was closed and has been the host to many different restaurants .
#Text=Later it was turned into a Mexican restaurant called " El Capri " .
#Text=After El Capri closed a single taco cart going by the same name sat outside the vacant building until they moved to San Martin ( just south of Morgan Hill on Monterey Rd . ) .
#Text=Now the building that once was a hot spot in the 50s where people went to dance , drink and eat(such as my grandparents ) , it sits vacant .
#Text=This historic landmark is certainly an eye catcher and is sad to see it not being used .

#Text=Be careful to check for ticks after hiking in fields in the bay area .
#Text=There is a high rate of lyme disease transmission in the Bay Area .
#Text=If a bulls ' eye rash develops at the tick bite site , immediately seek medical help and treatment with antibiotics .
